{"tid":175113,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"(牙你老母)有冇巴絲試過用漂牙機","createTime":"2017-03-27T09:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T13:32:43.000Z","uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ecccfed10b61beabb68420eeb2bd68c48aba979","tid":175113,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"今日睇蘋果動介紹家用漂牙機<br />\n有冇巴絲用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n效果work唔work<br />\n<br />\n我見佢介紹一部係韓國野一部係大陸野<br />\n韓國個部要一日用兩次 又要搽gel<br />\n大陸果部就方便d 3日用一次 而且係牙貼<br />\n但大陸野好驚有伏<br />\n<br />\n5 6 百蚊好似又屌得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去診所漂一次成千千聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8caca4bf910fa6b9692a74e7e0dddb1e72dcaf","tid":175113,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5987d82ee555f9f7e788f65f6b2310751e3bb234","tid":175113,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T13:32:43.000Z","msg":"用左泡菜嗰隻 斷斷續續用左半年<br />\n啲牙愈用愈敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家食凍少少都好易牙齒敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}